{"meta":{"title":"时光机","subtitle":null,"description":null,"author":"Monkey Zhu","url":"https://jason0307.github.io"},"pages":[{"title":"Categories","date":"2017-10-15T16:27:45.789Z","updated":"2017-10-15T16:23:38.789Z","comments":true,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"About","date":"2017-10-15T16:27:28.763Z","updated":"2017-10-15T16:23:38.784Z","comments":true,"path":"about/index.html","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/about/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"Tags","date":"2017-10-15T16:28:02.597Z","updated":"2017-10-15T16:23:38.795Z","comments":true,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"知足","slug":"知足","date":"2018-07-02T13:27:00.000Z","updated":"2018-07-03T15:26:10.679Z","comments":true,"path":"2018/07/02/知足/","link":"","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/2018/07/02/知足/","excerpt":"","text":"面色温柔，活得简单，不去占有，这就是最好的生活。","categories":[{"name":"摘抄","slug":"摘抄","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/categories/摘抄/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生活感悟","slug":"生活感悟","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/tags/生活感悟/"}]},{"title":"何处是停歇","slug":"Monkey-Zhu","date":"2017-10-15T17:27:00.000Z","updated":"2018-07-03T15:27:49.003Z","comments":true,"path":"2017/10/16/Monkey-Zhu/","link":"","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/2017/10/16/Monkey-Zhu/","excerpt":"","text":"每次听到那句“想得太多， 又做的太少”， 心中都会有别样的感动。 身边的人总会在大浪里渐渐流失， 越走越少。 但内心却一定是越来越丰盈的。 无论你选择远走他乡， 还是选择安逸平和， 奔放如河， 货涓涓如溪。 活的都是一个【心气】。 心气高了， 人会傲， 容易摔跟头。 心气低了， 人会卑， 容易脆弱。 只有心气平了， 淡了， 一切才会如流水顺畅。 不以物喜， 不以己悲， 大抵如此了吧。","categories":[{"name":"摘抄","slug":"摘抄","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/categories/摘抄/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生活感悟","slug":"生活感悟","permalink":"https://jason0307.github.io/tags/生活感悟/"}]}]}